kirītinam—with helmets; gadinam—with maces; cakriņam—with discs; ca—
and; tejorāśim—effulgence; sarvatah—all sides; dīptimantam—glowing;
pasyāmi—I see; tvām—You; durnirīkṣyam—difficult to see; samantāt—
